Fig. 5L
) screlotized, consisting of penis and accessory piece, composition of male copulatory organ of our specimen damaged during preparation. Penis long, length 138. Accessory piece (
Fig. 5L
) rodshaped with bifurcated base and widened tip, length 60. Vagina unsclerotized.

